#LanguageDetection
defdetect_languages(df,tokenizer,model,label_map,text_col="lyrics",batch_size=64):
texts=df[text_col].tolist()
languages=[]
total=len(texts)
foriinrange(0,total,batch_size):
batch=texts[i:i+batch_size]
cleaned=[t[:512]ifisinstance(t,str)else""fortinbatch]
inputs=tokenizer(cleaned,return_tensors="pt",padding=True,truncation=True).to(device)
withtorch.no_grad():
logits=model(**inputs).logits
preds=torch.argmax(F.softmax(logits,dim=1),dim=1)
fortext,predinzip(cleaned,preds.tolist()):
ifnotisinstance(text,str)ornottext.strip():
languages.append("unknown")
else:
languages.append(label_map[str(pred)])
print(f"Processed{min(i+batch_size,total)}/{total}rows")
returnlanguages

loss_fn=CrossEntropyLoss()

emb_p=model(p_tok)['sentence_embedding']
emb_s=model(s_tok)['sentence_embedding']
sims=torch.matmul(emb_p,emb_s.T)
labels=torch.arange(sims.size(0),device=device)
loss=loss_fn(sims,labels)

loss.backward()
optimizer.step()

#RetrievewithNumericBoost
defretrieve_with_numeric_boost(prompt:str,top_k:int=20,alpha:float=0.8):
user_emb=embed_prompt(prompt)
